summary: Pics from last night’s Let’s Go Eevee gameplay! It’s so much fun and I love it! I had hoped it would have gone on sale at Black...
caption:
Pics from last night’s Let’s Go Eevee gameplay! It’s so much fun and I love it! I had hoped it would have gone on sale at Black Friday or Cyber Monday (and unfortunately it wasn’t) but definitely worth the $60 it cost to get this game and I regret nothing! 💰😰😂🤣 I was getting it whether it was on sale, one way or another. 😂🎮⚡️💸 Also, Eevee is so cute, btw! Decided to name her Lily, named after the actress Lily James from Mamma Mia 2, lol! 😅🎶 Why am I so obsessed with Mamma Mia lately? Haha! 😂🤣 I might play it again tonight! It’s a really good game! I highly recommend it, if you love Pokémon! 🤩😍🎮👍
